    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><span>The end of this wand is forked instead of tapered.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell; <strong>Frequency</strong> once per day, plus overcharge; This activation takes <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span> if the spell normally takes <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> to cast, or <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">T</span> if the spell normally takes <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span>; <strong>Effect</strong> You Cast the Spell, and increase its area. Add 5 feet to the radius of a burst that normally has a radius of at least 10 feet; add 5 feet to the length of a cone or line that is normally 15 feet long or smaller; or add 10 feet to the length of a larger cone or line.<br /></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply a casting of a spell of the appropriate level. The spell must have a casting time of <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">A</span> or <span style=\"font-family: 'Pathfinder2eActions'; font-size: 1.8em; display: inline;\">D</span>, can&rsquo;t have a duration, and must have an area of burst (10 feet or more), cone, or line.</span></p>",
